(97, '03/16/2015', 25, 'Tootay huwy dil se piyar karo gi', 'tootay_huwy_dil_se_piyar_karo_gi', 'Boy : Tootay huwy dil se piyar karo gi,<br /><br />Ya dil tootny tak piyar karo gi.<br /><br /><br />Girl : Kameeny!<br /><br />Tooti hui chappal se pitay ga,<br /><br />Ya chappal k tootny tak pitay ga....:-)', '9', 'Active', 3, 'Boy : Tootay huwy dil se piyar karo gi,\n\nYa dil tootny tak piyar karo gi.\n\n\nGirl : Kameeny!\n\nTooti hui chappal se pitay ga,\n\nYa chappal k tootny tak pitay ga....:-)', 'Tootay huwy dil se piyar karo gi', '2015-04-22 14:44:25'),
