(99, '03/15/2015', 1, 'For Women:To be happy with a man', 'for_womento_be_happy_with_a_man', 'For Women:To be happy with a man<br />you must understand him a lot and love him a little.<br />For Man:To be happy with a woman<br />you must love her a lot and not try to understand her at all.<br />', '7', 'Active', 4, 'you must understand him a lot and love him a little.\nFor Man:To be happy with a woman\nyou must love her a lot and not try to understand her at all.', 'For Women:To be happy with a man, sms, woman\'s day sms', '2015-04-17 18:08:42'),
