(105, '03/16/2015', 24, 'Happy Easter to My Best Friend!', 'happy_easter_to_my_best_friend', 'The Easter feeling does not end,<br />it signals a new beggining of nature spring<br />and brand new life of friendship.<br />Happy Easter to My Best Friend!<br />', '9', 'Active', 6, 'The Easter feeling does not end,\nit signals a new beggining of nature spring\nand brand new life of friendship.\nHappy Easter to My Best Friend!\n', 'Happy Easter to My Best Friend', '2015-04-07 05:33:03'),
(106, '03/16/2015', 24, 'Wishing U a Very \"HAPPY EASTER\"', 'wishing_u_a_very_happy_easter', 'Wishing U a Very \"HAPPY EASTER\"<br />Wid Luv And Best Wishes..<br />May That EASTER Day Brings<br />LOT of Happiness And JOYS in ur LIFE.<br />May u Live Long LIFE...<br />And That EASTER day Will comes in UR life Hundred Times...<br />Remember me in ur prayers..', '9', 'Active', 8, 'Wishing U a Very \"HAPPY EASTER\"\nWid Luv And Best Wishes..\nMay That EASTER Day Brings\nLOT of Happiness And JOYS in ur LIFE.\nMay u Live Long LIFE...\nAnd That EASTER day Will comes in UR life Hundred Times...\nRemember me in ur prayers..', 'Wishing U a Very HAPPY EASTER', '2015-04-20 19:33:26'),
(107, '03/16/2015', 31, 'Smiles of Happy Sunshine', 'smiles_of_happy_sunshine', 'Smiles of happy sunshine,<br />Arms of everlasting luv,<br />Touch of sweet roses,<br />There is magic in the air<br />Whenever ur there,<br />Mother, everything to U I owe,<br />May all pleasures of life come ur way.<br />\"Happy Mother\'s day\"', '4', 'Active', 6, 'Smiles of happy sunshine, mothers day sms', 'Smiles of happy sunshine, mothers day sms', '2015-04-22 19:24:19'),
(108, '03/16/2015', 31, 'Mother, I Love You', 'mother_i_love_you', 'Mother, I love you,<br />For all that you do.<br />I\'ll kiss you and hug you,<br />Because you love me, too.<br />You feed me and need me,<br />To teach you to play,<br />So smile because I love you,<br />On this Mother\'s Day', '4', 'Active', 4, 'Mother, I love you, mothers day sms', 'Mother, I love you, mothers day sms', '2015-04-23 06:57:08'),
(109, '03/16/2015', 31, 'My Mother, My Friend So Dear', 'my_mother_my_friend_so_dear', 'My Mother, my friend so dear<br /><br />Throughout my life you\'re always near<br /><br />A tender smile to guide my way<br /><br />You\'re the sunshine to light my day', '4', 'Active', 3, 'My Mother, my friend so dear, mothers day sms', 'My Mother, my friend so dear, mothers day sms', '2015-04-19 05:36:40'),
(111, '03/16/2015', 31, 'A Mother\'s Work Is Never Done', 'a_mothers_work_is_never_done', 'A mother\'s work is never done<br />She works from morning until dawn<br />She spreads her love<br />And keeps you warm<br />But only once a year we say<br />Mother we wish you \"Happy Mothers Day\"', '4', 'Active', 5, 'A mother\'s work is never done, mothers day sms', 'A mother\'s work is never done, mothers day sms', '2015-04-18 07:43:19'),
(115, '03/16/2015', 31, 'Mother Is An Undying Love', 'mother_is_an_undying_love', 'Mother is an undying love,<br />A love beyond compare,<br />the one you take your troubles to,<br />she is the one who really cares.<br />Mother you are all of this and more,<br />I love you very much', '4', 'Active', 4, 'Mother Is An Undying Love, mothers day sms', 'Mother Is An Undying Love, mothers day sms', '2015-04-17 02:21:01'),
(116, '03/16/2015', 31, 'Who Ran To Help Me When I Fell', 'who_ran_to_help_me_when_i_fell', 'Who ran to help me when I fell,<br /><br />And would some pretty story tell,<br /><br />Or kiss the place to make it well?<br /><br />My Mother.<br /><br />(*) Happy Mother\'s Day (*)', '4', 'Active', 3, 'Who Ran To Help Me When I Fell, mothers day sms', 'Who Ran To Help Me When I Fell, mothers day sms', '2015-04-16 16:47:02'),
(117, '03/16/2015', 31, 'A Mother Serves Her Sugar', 'a_mother_serves_her_sugar', 'A mother serves her sugar with<br />A bit of peppermint<br />To clarify the passages<br />That carry what she meant<br />When she first set to bear a soul<br />Quite separate from her own,<br />Whom she would cherish, yet must teach<br />To live and die alone.', '4', 'Active', 5, 'A mother serves her sugar, mothers day sms', 'A mother serves her sugar, , mothers day sms', '2015-04-15 14:43:58'),
(119, '03/16/2015', 31, 'Happy Mother\'s Day Means More Than Flowers', 'happy_mothers_day_means_more_than_flowers', 'Happy Mother\'s Day<br /><br />means more than flowers and gifts<br /><br />It means saying thank you<br /><br />It means I love you<br /><br />You are my mother, my friend<br /><br />Today is your day!', '4', 'Active', 6, 'Happy Mother\'s Day means more than flowers, mothers day ', 'Happy Mother\'s Day means more than flowers, mothers day ', '2015-04-19 15:20:53'),
(120, '03/16/2015', 31, 'It Spells Mother', 'it_spells_mother', 'Many hugs<br />Only love never anger<br />Teaching me<br />Helping me<br />Every smile when I was sad<br />Raising me to be strong<br /><br />It spells Mother. Thanks for being u', '4', 'Active', 8, 'It spells Mother, mothers day sms', 'It spells Mother, mothers day sms', '2015-04-16 04:51:43'),
(121, '03/16/2015', 31, 'Mother Love Is The Fuel', 'mother_love_is_the_fuel', 'Mother love is the fuel that<br /><br />enables a normal human being<br /><br />to do the impossible.', '4', 'Active', 4, 'Mother love is the fuel, mothers day sms', 'Mother love is the fuel, mothers day sms', '2015-04-19 04:24:55'),
(122, '03/16/2015', 31, 'Being A Full-Time Mother . . . Highest Salaried Job', 'being_a_full_time_mother_highest_salaried_job', 'Being a full-time mother is<br /><br />one of the highest salaried jobs...<br /><br />since the payment is pure love.<br />                                (Mildred B. Vermont)', '4', 'Active', 5, 'Being a full-time mother . . . highest salaried job, mothers day sms', 'Being a full-time mother . . . highest salaried job, mothers day sms', '2015-04-16 22:51:58'),
(123, '03/16/2015', 31, 'Mom Makes Me Feel Cafe & Calm', 'mom_makes_me_feel_cafe_calm', 'I luv u mom<br />having u makes me feel safe & calm<br />I miss u mom<br />Missing touches 2 my face with ur chapped palm<br />u r the greatest<br />because u r my mom', '4', 'Active', 4, 'Mom makes me feel safe & calm, mothers day sms', 'Mom makes me feel safe & calm, mothers day sms', '2015-04-19 01:44:40'),
(124, '03/16/2015', 31, 'Mothers Day Poem MSG', 'mothers_day_poem_msg', 'Hundreds of stars in the pretty sky,<br />Hundreds of shells on the shore together,<br /><br />Hundreds of birds that go singing by,<br />Hundreds of lambs in the sunny weather.<br /><br />Hundreds of dewdrops to greet the dawn,<br />Hundreds of bees in the purple clover,<br /><br />Hundreds of butterflies on the lawn,<br />But only one mother the world wide over.', '4', 'Active', 22, 'Mothers Day Poem MSG, mothers day sms', 'Mothers Day Poem MSG, mothers day sms', '2015-04-23 23:10:46'),
(125, '03/16/2015', 31, 'Happy Mothers Day From Son / Daughter', 'happy_mothers_day_from_son_daughter', 'Thank you mom for everything that you have done<br />and<br />keeping doing for me.<br />Thank you God for having you as part of my life,<br />you have taught me many good things,<br />today what i have become it’s because of you.<br /><br />Wishing you Happy Mother\'s Day', '4', 'Active', 4, 'Happy Mothers Day From Son / Daughter, Mothers day sms', 'Happy Mothers Day From Son / Daughter, Mothers day sms', '2015-04-22 23:04:53'),
(126, '03/16/2015', 31, '4 Lines of Mothers Day Poetry', '4_lines_of_mothers_day_poetry', 'My mother is a special part<br /><br />Of all that’s cherished in my heart,<br /><br />She is my pearl, my soul, my mate;<br /><br />She is the one to make life great.<br /><br />She is an angel without the wings!', '4', 'Active', 3, '4 Lines of Mothers Day Poetry, Mothers Day sms', '4 Lines of Mothers Day Poetry, Mothers Day sms', '2015-04-19 20:16:55'),
(127, '03/16/2015', 31, 'Mothers Day Quote by Stevie Wonder', 'mothers_day_quote_by_stevie_wonder', 'Mama was my greatest teacher,<br />a teacher of compassion, love and fearlessness.<br />If love is sweet as a flower,<br />then my mother is that sweet flower of love.<br />                                            ~Stevie Wonder', '4', 'Active', 5, 'Mothers Day Quote by Stevie Wonder, Mothers Day sms', 'Mothers Day Quote by Stevie Wonder, Mothers Day sms', '2015-04-20 01:46:11'),
(128, '03/16/2015', 31, 'Immeasurable Contribution To My Life', 'immeasurable_contribution_to_my_life', 'I take this opportunity<br />to thank you for<br />your immeasurable<br />contribution to my life.<br />Thank you Mom!<br />And wish you a<br />Very Happy Mother\'s Day!', '4', 'Active', 6, 'Immeasurable Contribution To My Life, Mothers Day sms', 'Immeasurable Contribution To My Life, Mothers Day sms', '2015-04-22 19:54:19'),
(129, '03/16/2015', 31, 'Essay on Mother', 'essay_on_mother', 'In an exam,<br />chldrn wer gvn to write an esay on mother.<br /><br />A cute child wrote:<br /><br />\"combination of million wrds<br />4m 26 alphabets<br />can never express my loving mom.\":-)', '4', 'Active', 5, 'Essay on mother, Mothers day sms', 'Essay on mother, Mothers day sms', '2015-04-22 15:44:25'),
(130, '03/16/2015', 31, 'I Love My Mother Beyond Limits', 'i_love_my_mother_beyond_limits', 'Your mother bore you<br />For 9 months ,<br />She watched her feet<br />Swell, she struggled to<br />Climb stairs,<br />She got breathless quick,<br />She bore excruciating pain,<br />She suffered many sleepless<br />Nights,<br />She became your nurse, your<br />Chef, your teacher, your<br />Cleaner, your launderette, your<br />Friend.<br />She struggled for you, but not<br />Did she see it as a struggle,<br />Not once did she develop<br />Regrets after all this ...<br />How dare you say even<br />\"uff\" to her ...', '4', 'Active', 3, 'I love my mother beyond limits, Mothers Day sms', 'I love my mother beyond limits, Mothers Day sms', '2015-04-22 13:26:18'),
(131, '03/16/2015', 31, 'Mothers Love Knows No Boundaries', 'mothers_love_knows_no_boundaries', 'Mothers love knows no boundaries<br />As it grows healthier each day,<br /><br />Knows no reason as it is given unconditionally,<br /><br />Knows no season as it<br />Transcends forever through eternity...<br /><br />Happy mother\'s day', '4', 'Active', 4, 'Mothers love knows no boundaries, Mothers day sms', 'Mothers love knows no boundaries, Mothers day sms', '2015-04-18 12:22:19'),
