(258, '03/17/2015', 27, 'Kash mein tere Haseen Hath ka kanGan hota', 'kash_mein_tere_haseen_hath_ka_kangan_hota', 'Kash mein tere Haseen Hath ka Kangan hota.<br /><br />T0 Baray pyar sy baray Maan k sath..<br /><br />Apne Nazuk c kalaai mein charhati mujh k0 ..<br /><br />Aur Be-tabi sy furqt kay khazaan Lamhoon mein <br /><br />T0 kise Soch mein Doobi jo Ghumati mujh ko <br /><br />Mein tere hath ki khushboo sy mehek sa jata,<br /><br />Jab kabhi m00d Mein Aakar mujhe Choma krti.<br /><br />Tere honton ki mein heDDat sY Dahk sajata ..<br /><br />Raat ko jab bhi nend00n ky Safr Pr Jati<br /><br />Murmareen Hath ka ik takeia Bnaya krti <br /><br />Men tere Kaan sy Lag kr kai Batein krta..<br /><br />Teri Zulfon ko tere Gal k0 choma krta <br /><br />Jab bhi tu band-e-qeba kholny lagti Janaan..<br /><br />Apni Aankhon ko tere Hussan sy khera krta <br /><br />Mujh k0 be-taB sa rakhta tere chaht ka nasha <br /><br />Mein tere RooH ky Gulshan mein Mahkta Rahta <br /><br />Men tere jesam ky AanGan mein khankata Rahta <br /><br />Kuch nhe t0 Yahi Be-NAAM sa bandhan hota <br /><br />KASH MEN TERE HASEEN HATHON KA KANgAN HOTa. ', '6', 'Active', 4, 'Kash mein tere Haseen Hath ka Kangan hota.\n\nT0 Baray pyar sy baray Maan k sath..\n\nApne Nazuk c kalaai mein charhati mujh k0 ..\n\nAur Be-tabi sy furqt kay khazaan Lamhoon mein \n\nT0 kise Soch mein Doobi jo Ghumati mujh ko \n\nMein tere hath ki khushboo sy mehek sa jata,\n\nJab kabhi m00d Mein Aakar mujhe Choma krti.\n\nTere honton ki mein heDDat sY Dahk sajata ..\n\nRaat ko jab bhi nend00n ky Safr Pr Jati\n\nMurmareen Hath ka ik takeia Bnaya krti \n\nMen tere Kaan sy Lag kr kai Batein krta..\n\nTeri Zulfon ko tere Gal k0 choma krta \n\nJab bhi tu band-e-qeba kholny lagti Janaan..\n\nApni Aankhon ko tere Hussan sy khera krta \n\nMujh k0 be-taB sa rakhta tere chaht ka nasha \n\nMein tere RooH ky Gulshan mein Mahkta Rahta \n\nMen tere jesam ky AanGan mein khankata Rahta \n\nKuch nhe t0 Yahi Be-NAAM sa bandhan hota \n\nKASH MEN TE