(259, '03/17/2015', 36, 'Ik larki, Pagli si, Diwani si,', 'ik_larki_pagli_si_diwani_si', 'Ik larki,<br />Pagli si, Diwani si,<br />Masoom si, Anjaani si,<br />Apne ghar ki mundair per bethi,<br />In galiyon aur chobaaron ko,<br />In koochon aur bazaaron ko,<br />Dekhti hai..<br />Jahan us ne apna bachpan guzara tha,<br />Us ki aankhon mein tha,<br />Intizaar..<br />Kisi ka!<br />Magar usey kaun samjhaye,<br />Ke bachpan ke vaadey to,<br />Kacchi dor ki tarah hote hain,<br />aur,<br />Bhala jane waley,<br />Kab laut kar atey hain..', '6', 'Active', 5, 'Ik larki,\nPagli si, Diwani si,\nMasoom si, Anjaani si,\nApne ghar ki mundair per bethi,\nIn galiyon aur chobaaron ko,\nIn koochon aur bazaaron ko,\nDekhti hai..\nJahan us ne apna bachpan guzara tha,\nUs ki aankhon mein tha,\nIntizaar..\nKisi ka!\nMagar usey kaun samjhaye,\nKe bachpan ke vaadey to,\nKacchi dor ki tarah hote hain,\naur,\nBhala jane waley,\nKab laut kar atey hain..', 'larki, Pagli , Diwani, Masoom, Anjaani ', '2015-04-22 01:35:04'),
(260, '03/17/2015', 32, 'Tere dil main ho mera ghar ', 'tere_dil_main_ho_mera_ghar', 'Tere dil main ho mera ghar yeh zaroori to nahi,<br />meri aahon main ho asar yeh zaroori to nahi...<br />Chand suraj ho mere hamsafar phir bhee, <br />mere ghar main ho sehar yeh zaroori to nahi...<br />Tere kafilay main ho lakhon tere chhahnay walay, <br />main tujh say jaoun bichher yeh zaroori to nahi...<br />kush to hai seenay main jisko zuba na mili, <br />mere saath tu bhee jaye bikhar yeh zaroori to nahi...<br />Tum phool ho to kaya hum bhee nasoor hai, <br />tujhi pay ho sab ki nazar yeh zaroori to nahi...<br />bhar kay ashq aankho main unko jatay dekha hai, <br />giry yaha aansu wo meri ho kabar yeh zaroori to nahi...<br />mana khushiyon pay hai unka ikhtiyaar zalim <br />gham bhee ho mujh say bekhabar yeh zaroori to nahi...', '6', 'Active', 3, 'Tere dil main ho mera ghar yeh zaroori to nahi,\nmeri aahon main ho asar yeh zaroori to nahi...\nChand suraj ho mere hamsafar phir bhee, \nmere ghar main ho sehar yeh zaroori to nahi...\nTere kafilay main ho lakhon tere chhahnay walay, \nmain tujh say jaoun bichher yeh zaroori to nahi...\nkush to hai seenay main jisko zuba na mili, \nmere saath tu bhee jaye bikhar yeh zaroori to nahi...\nTum phool ho to kaya hum bhee nasoor hai, \ntujhi pay ho sab ki nazar yeh zaroori to nahi...\nbhar kay ashq aankho main unko jatay dekha hai, \ngiry yaha aansu wo meri ho kabar yeh zaroori to nahi...\nmana khushiyon pay hai unka ikhtiyaar zalim \ngham bhee ho mujh say bekhabar yeh zaroori to nahi...', 'dil ,ghar, chaand, sooraj, suraj, hamsafar', '2015-04-21 19:04:15'),
(261, '03/17/2015', 36, 'Mein Aadmi hoon aam sa', 'mein_aadmi_hoon_aam_sa', 'Mein Aadmi hoon aam sa<br />Ek Qissa na-tamam sa.<br />Na lehja be-misal hai<br />Na baat mein kamal hai<br />Hoon dekhney mein aam sa<br />Udasion ki shaam sa,<br />jaisey k ek raaz hoon<br />Khud se be-niaz hoon<br />Na mehjabeeno se Rabt hai<br />Na Shuhraton ka zabt hai<br />Ranjha na qais hoon<br />Insha na Faiz hoon<br />Mei paiker-e-ikhlas hoon<br />Wafa, dua aur aas hoon<br />Mein shakhs khud-shnas hoon<br />TUM HI KARO KOI FAISLA !<br />Mei aadmi hoon AAM sa !!<br />Ya<br />Phir bohat hi \"KHAAS\" hoon !!!', '6', 'Active', 6, 'Mein Aadmi hoon aam sa\nEk Qissa na-tamam sa.\nNa lehja be-misal hai\nNa baat mein kamal hai\nHoon dekhney mein aam sa\nUdasion ki shaam sa,\njaisey k ek raaz hoon\nKhud se be-niaz hoon\nNa mehjabeeno se Rabt hai\nNa Shuhraton ka zabt hai\nRanjha na qais hoon\nInsha na Faiz hoon\nMei paiker-e-ikhlas hoon\nWafa, dua aur aas hoon\nMein shakhs khud-shnas hoon\nTUM HI KARO KOI FAISLA !\nMei aadmi hoon AAM sa !!\nYa\nPhir bohat hi \"KHAAS\" hoon !!!', 'Aadmi, aam, qissa, be-misaal', '2015-04-22 06:33:42'),
(262, '03/17/2015', 32, 'Shukriya', 'shukriya', 'Ye Raah-e-Wafa Ki Saleb Par<br />Do Qadam Chalnay Ka Shukriya<br />Bara Pur Khatar Tha Ye Raasta<br />Tere Loat Jaanay Ka Shukriya<br />Teri Yaad Jaanay Kis Bhais Main<br />Meri Rag-o-Jaan Main Dhal Gai<br />Ye Kamal Hai Teri Yaad Ka<br />Mujhe Yaad Aanay Ka Shukriya<br />Mujhe Khasta Haal Sa Dekh Kar<br />Tere Phool Se Hont Khil Uthay<br />Mujhe Gham Nahin Jo Kaho Gay<br />Teri Is Adakaari Ka Shukriya', '6', 'Active', 5, 'Ye Raah-e-Wafa Ki Saleb Par\nDo Qadam Chalnay Ka Shukriya\nBara Pur Khatar Tha Ye Raasta\nTere Loat Jaanay Ka Shukriya\nTeri Yaad Jaanay Kis Bhais Main\nMeri Rag-o-Jaan Main Dhal Gai\nYe Kamal Hai Teri Yaad Ka\nMujhe Yaad Aanay Ka Shukriya\nMujhe Khasta Haal Sa Dekh Kar\nTere Phool Se Hont Khil Uthay\nMujhe Gham Nahin Jo Kaho Gay\nTeri Is Adakaari Ka Shukriya', 'Raah-e-wafa, shukriya, rasta', '2015-04-21 12:29:53'),
(263, '03/17/2015', 36, 'Mere Wajood Ki Mujh Main', 'mere_wajood_ki_mujh_main', 'Mere Wajood Ki Mujh Main Talash Chor Gaya<br />Jo Puri Na Ho Kabhi Aesi Aas Chor Gaya<br />Yehi Karam Nawazi Uski Mujh Pe Kam Hae Kiya<br />Ke Khud To Door Hai Yaden Pas Chor Gaya<br />Jo Khawahishen Theen Kabhi Hasraton Main Dhal Gayeen Ab<br />Mere Labon Pe Wo Ek Lafz Kaash Chor Gaya<br />Ye Mera Zarf Hai K Ek Roz Usne Mujh Se Kaha<br />Ke Aam Logon Main Ek Mujhko Khas Chor Gaya<br />Baharon Se Mujhe Isi Liye To Nafrat Hai<br />Inhi Ruton Main Mujhe Wo Udaas Chor Gaya...', '6', 'Active', 4, 'Mere Wajood Ki Mujh Main Talash Chor Gaya\nJo Puri Na Ho Kabhi Aesi Aas Chor Gaya\nYehi Karan Nawazi Uski Mujh Pe Kam Hae Kiya\nKe Khud To Door Hai Yaden Pas Chor Gaya\nJo Khawahishen Theen Kabhi Hasraton Main Dhal Gayeen Ab\nMere Labon Pe Wo Ek Lafz Kaash Chor Gaya\nYe Mera Zarf Hai K Ek Roz Usne Mujh Se Kaha\nKe Aam Logon Main Ek Mujhko Khas Chor Gaya\nBaharon Se Mujhe Isi Liye To Nafrat Hai\nInhi Ruton Main Mujhe Wo Udaas Chor Gaya', 'Talash, talaash, wajood, aas,', '2015-04-22 04:47:35'),
(264, '03/17/2015', 32, 'Ab so jao', 'ab_so_jao', 'Q Jagtay ho, kya sochtay ho<br />Kuch hum se kaho,<br />Tanha na raho,<br />socha na karo,<br />Yadon k barastay badal ko,<br />Palkon pe sajana theek nahi,<br />Jo apne bas ki baat na ho,<br />Us ko dohrana theek nahi,<br />Ab raat ki aankhain bheeg chaleen,<br />Or chand bhi hai chup jaane ko,<br />Kuch dair main shabnam aaye gi,<br />Phulon ki pyas bujhaye gi,<br />Khawabon k nagar main kho jao,<br />Ab so jao, Ab so jao.', '6', 'Active', 4, 'Q Jagtay ho, kya sochtay ho\nKuch hum se kaho,\nTanha na raho,\nsocha na karo,\nYadon k barastay badal ko,\nPalkon pe sajana theek nahi,\nJo apne bas ki baat na ho,\nUs ko dohrana theek nahi,\nAb raat ki aankhain bheeg chaleen,\nOr chand bhi hai chup jaane ko,\nKuch dair main shabnam aaye gi,\nPhulon ki pyas bujhaye gi,\nKhawabon k nagar main kho jao,\nAb so jao, Ab so jao.', 'Jagna, sona, shabnam, tanha, sochna', '2015-04-22 13:59:25'),
(265, '03/17/2015', 34, 'Hum Tum Tanha Bethay Hon', 'hum_tum_tanha_bethay_hon', 'Hum Tum Tanha Bethay Hon,<br />Or Halki Halki Barish Ho,<br />Kuch Kapkapatay Hont Hon,<br />Or Bheegi Bheegi Aankhain Hon,<br />Barish Ki Boondon Ka Koi Asar Na Ho,<br />Saanson Main Itni Garmi Ho,<br />Raat Ka Ho Sannaata Bhi,<br />Qadam Behekne Ka Dar Bhi Ho,<br />Sama Jayen Ek Dooje Main Hum,<br />Guzar Jayen Har Had Se Hum,<br />Madhosh Ho Jayen Pyar Main,<br />Mehek Jaye Wo Raat Bhi,<br />Kaash!Kabhi To Aisa Ho Ke,<br />Hum Tum Tanha Bethay Hon.', '6', 'Active', 6, 'Hum Tum Tanha Bethay Hon,\nOr Halki Halki Barish Ho,\nKuch Kapkapatay Hont Hon,\nOr Bheegi Bheegi Aankhain Hon,\nBarish Ki Boondon Ka Koi Asar Na Ho,\nSaanson Main Itni Garmi Ho,\nRaat Ka Ho Sannaata Bhi,\nQadam Behekne Ka Dar Bhi Ho,\nSama Jayen Ek Dooje Main Hum,\nGuzar Jayen Har Had Se Hum,\nMadhosh Ho Jayen Pyar Main,\nMehek Jaye Wo Raat Bhi,\nKaash!Kabhi To Aisa Ho Ke,\nHum Tum Tanha Bethay Hon.', 'Baarish, Tanha, Bheegi, Ankhain, kapkapatay', '2015-04-18 18:59:00'),
