(268, '03/17/2015', 36, 'Bichar Ke Tujh Se', 'bichar_ke_tujh_se', 'Bichar Ke Tujh Se Yehi Khud Ko Saza Di Main Ne,<br />Teri talaash main ek umar bita di main ne,<br />Tujhe jo dil se nakaala to yun laga mujhe,<br />Jaisay apne andar ki koi deewar gira di main ne,<br />Dil ka sheeshay pe jahan teri yaad basti thi,<br />Ap wahan waqt ki dhool jama di main ne,<br />Apne andar se bohot bar suna hai \"Main Yahan Hoon\",<br />\"Tu Kahan Hai, Tu kahan Hai\" ki jab bhi sada di main ne,<br />Us ko achaanak jo khoya to yoon laga jaisay,<br />Zindagi aik hi lamhay main ganwaa di main ne.', '6', 'Active', 6, 'Bichar Ke Tujh Se Yehi Khud Ko Saza Di Main Ne,\nTeri talaash main ek umar bita di main ne,\nTujhe jo dil se nakaala to yun laga mujhe,\nJaisay apne andar ki koi deewar gira di main ne,\nDil ka sheeshay pe jahan teri yaad basti thi,\nAp wahan waqt ki dhool jama di main ne,\nApne andar se bohot bar suna hai \"Main Yahan Hoon\",\n\"Tu Kahan Hai, Tu kahan Hai\" ki jab bhi sada di main ne,\nUs ko achaanak jo khoya to yoon laga jaisay,\nZindagi aik hi lamhay main ganwaa di main ne.', 'Bichar, Saza, talaash, umar, dewaar, kahan, zindagi.', '2015-04-24 05:15:51'),
(269, '03/17/2015', 34, 'Har Haseen Mosam Ki', 'har_haseen_mosam_ki', 'Har Haseen Mosam Ki,<br />har haseeen baarish main,<br />Dard tum jagaatay ho,<br />Bewajah sataatay ho,<br />Mosamon k lutf ko tum,<br />Dard main bahaatay ho,<br />Zindagi k naam se tum,<br />Jee mera jalaatay ho,<br />Lutf k sabhi lamhaay,<br />Yaadon main ganwatay ho,<br />Har Haseen Mosam Ki,<br />har haseeen baarish main,<br />Tum kiyun yaad aate ho.', '6', 'Active', 6, 'Har Haseen Mosam Ki,\nhar haseeen baarish main,\nDard tum jagaatay ho,\nBewajah sataatay ho,\nMosamon k lutf ko tum,\nDard main bahaatay ho,\nZindagi k naam se tum,\nJee mera jalaatay ho,\nLutf k sabhi lamhaay,\nYaadon main ganwatay ho,\nHar Haseen Mosam Ki,\nhar haseeen baarish main,\nTum kiyun yaad aate ho.', 'baarish, Haseen ,mosam, yaad, satatay, satana, jagatay,dard,zindagi', '2015-04-20 00:46:11'),
